Translations.Text: Their frater Lot dictus to them vos non est righteous
Ego non ask vos any wage my wage advenit unus Dominus universe
Perfecit vos habet generis vir totus people
Vos forsake uxor tuus Dominus created vos! Indeed vos transgressing people
They dictus vos refrain O Lot vos banished
He dictus ego deplore tuus actions
My Dominus save me my familia ex their works
Nos saved eum totus his familia
Nos showered them miserable shower quod terrible shower those warned
Hoc est lesson multus people non est believers
multus assuredly tuus Dominus est Almighty Merciful
